    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wildwood: Graveyard Defense</strong> is a whimsical, top-down wave defense game. Pop ghosts with your lantern, collect ecto to brew potions, and explore the graveyard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211180/extras/3489241ac66eb7847dd8bbcf5426b0c2.poster.avif?t=1769811469\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211180/extras/3489241ac66eb7847dd8bbcf5426b0c2.webm?t=1769811469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Potions:</strong> Buff your base stats with temporary potions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lanterns:</strong> Unlock new lanterns each with unique properties and effects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skills:</strong> Experiment with  permabuffs and create different builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore:</strong> Unlock new levels and discover secrets in your graveyard</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211180/extras/9271b29de7d652de046aaf69eb72475b.poster.avif?t=1769811469\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211180/extras/9271b29de7d652de046aaf69eb72475b.webm?t=1769811469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced active combat with simple controls (not an auto-shooter)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mix of casual fun, sometimes chaotic situations, and a little bit of strategy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >End-game challenges and high-score leaderboards</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211180/extras/5bdcf2f7e5a81508e47c4a7c19e42547.poster.avif?t=1769811469\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211180/extras/5bdcf2f7e5a81508e47c4a7c19e42547.webm?t=1769811469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi, I'm Alan and I'm so excited for you to play Wildwood! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm a solo indie developer. I originally launched a prototype version of Wildwood on mobile in 2019 and decided to take the next step and make it a full game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm expanding the original gameplay, adding new mechanics, new enemies, and an entirely new progression system. I'm also working on some end-game content for anyone who wants even more challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please wishlist, and stay tuned for more!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
